summary:
Employee, from West LA VA, called clinic on 11/08/12 to report someone in the LA Clinic has been using the name and Social Security number of a Veteran who 
lives in Fort Smith. Patient was contacted by West LA employee and found at that time he had never been in the Los Angeles area. The person in LA is using 
Patient's A ID and Social Security number is a homeless man, no contact information is available. The VA ID picture which was taken in August, 2012, at the West 
LAVA is not Patient A. West LA employee wanted us to be aware that she has contacted the LAVA police and she will also contact IG. Patient A also presented 
to clinic on 11/7/12 with names and phone numbers of employees from West LAVA that has contacted him.

victim.victim_id: United States Department of Veterans Affairs
